{"tid":1627281,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【睇片】10.1 灣仔衝突片段　法新社記者：防暴警向橋下示威者投擲垃圾筒","createTime":"2019-10-05T15:14:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T15:40:17.000Z","uid":56321,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"03fd2b07e94b9e8048c16ecfb4f4fd9fa072a1e4","tid":1627281,"uid":56321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T15:14:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%9D%87%E7%89%87-10-1-%E7%81%A3%E4%BB%94%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81%E7%89%87%E6%AE%B5-%E6%B3%95%E6%96%B0%E7%A4%BE%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85-%E9%98%B2%E6%9A%B4%E8%AD%A6%E5%90%91%E6%A9%8B%E4%B8%8B%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E6%8A%95%E6%93%B2%E5%9E%83%E5%9C%BE%E7%AD%92/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%259D%2587%25E7%2589%2587-10-1-%25E7%2581%25A3%25E4%25BB%2594%25E8%25A1%259D%25E7%25AA%2581%25E7%2589%2587%25E6%25AE%25B5-%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%2596%25B0%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E8%25A8%2598%25E8%2580%2585-%25E9%2598%25B2%25E6%259A%25B4%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2590%2591%25E6%25A9%258B%25E4%25B8%258B%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E8%2580%2585%25E6%258A%2595%25E6%2593%25B2%25E5%259E%2583%25E5%259C%25BE%25E7%25AD%2592%2F&d=AECyLZWdcqpY%2FGgvZN2GpEx5KyfgaA76LUEybGJClr4%3D&h=b56d848b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%259D%2587%25E7%2589%2587-10-1-%25E7%2581%25A3%25E4%25BB%2594%25E8%25A1%259D%25E7%25AA%2581%25E7%2589%2587%25E6%25AE%25B5-%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%2596%25B0%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E8%25A8%2598%25E8%2580%2585-%25E9%2598%25B2%25E6%259A%25B4%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2590%2591%25E6%25A9%258B%25E4%25B8%258B%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E8%2580%2585%25E6%258A%2595%25E6%2593%25B2%25E5%259E%2583%25E5%259C%25BE%25E7%25AD%2592%2F&h=6ee968d3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%9D%87%E7%89%87-10-1-%E7%81%A3%E4%BB%94%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81%E7%89%87%E6%AE%B5-%E6%B3%95%E6%96%B0%E7%A4%BE%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85-%E9%98%B2%E6%9A%B4%E8%AD%A6%E5%90%91%E6%A9%8B%E4%B8%8B%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E6%8A%95%E6%93%B2%E5%9E%83%E5%9C%BE%E7%AD%92/</a><br />\n<br />\n今日法新社記者在個人 twitter 上載一段拍攝於 10.1 的短片，顯示防暴警察曾於灣仔行人天橋上，向橋底走在催淚煙霧中的示威者投擲一個橙色垃圾筒，其後又在橋上向馬路發射多枚催淚彈。但片段未能顯示有否示威者被該垃圾筒擊中受傷。<br />\n<br />\n《法新社》記者 Yan Zhao 今天在個人 twitter 戶口上載一段 45 秒短片，指是於 10 月 1 日拍攝。片段拍攝的現場為灣仔告士打道及通往入境事務大樓的行人天橋，畫面所見，當時告士打道已煙霧彌漫，而示威者則打開雨傘，嘗試往銅鑼灣方向急步撤退。期間多名持盾及長槍的防暴警察於行人天橋上出現，似乎已控制該天橋。突然一名戴黑色頭盔的警員將橋上一個橙色垃圾筒投擲向下面正撤離的示威者，並傳來巨響。由於煙霧彌漫，畫面未能顯示有否示威者被擊中。其後橋上警員多次向橋下發射催淚彈，槍聲四起，示威者爭相走避。"},{"pid":"7bb0bdf2abaa25dad6cb1540dd7bc6ac2f36cd10","tid":1627281,"uid":56321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T15:15:51.000Z","msg":"睇片 <br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%9D%87%E7%89%87-10-1-%E7%81%A3%E4%BB%94%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81%E7%89%87%E6%AE%B5-%E6%B3%95%E6%96%B0%E7%A4%BE%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85-%E9%98%B2%E6%9A%B4%E8%AD%A6%E5%90%91%E6%A9%8B%E4%B8%8B%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E6%8A%95%E6%93%B2%E5%9E%83%E5%9C%BE%E7%AD%92/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%259D%2587%25E7%2589%2587-10-1-%25E7%2581%25A3%25E4%25BB%2594%25E8%25A1%259D%25E7%25AA%2581%25E7%2589%2587%25E6%25AE%25B5-%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%2596%25B0%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E8%25A8%2598%25E8%2580%2585-%25E9%2598%25B2%25E6%259A%25B4%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2590%2591%25E6%25A9%258B%25E4%25B8%258B%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E8%2580%2585%25E6%258A%2595%25E6%2593%25B2%25E5%259E%2583%25E5%259C%25BE%25E7%25AD%2592%2F&d=AECyLZWdcqpY%2FGgvZN2GpEx5KyfgaA76LUEybGJClr4%3D&h=b56d848b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%259D%2587%25E7%2589%2587-10-1-%25E7%2581%25A3%25E4%25BB%2594%25E8%25A1%259D%25E7%25AA%2581%25E7%2589%2587%25E6%25AE%25B5-%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%2596%25B0%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E8%25A8%2598%25E8%2580%2585-%25E9%2598%25B2%25E6%259A%25B4%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2590%2591%25E6%25A9%258B%25E4%25B8%258B%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E8%2580%2585%25E6%258A%2595%25E6%2593%25B2%25E5%2